      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASHED UP HAVEN (1) goes very well this course and distance starting 10 times for five wins and five minors. Scored by 0.8 lengths last time (19.79) in a Grade 5 over 366m at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. RUPESH (2) goes very well at this journey having never missed the frame including seven wins. Recorded a 3.5 lengths win (19.79) in a Restricted WIN last time at this track. Looks one of the chances. ZIPPING URBAN (5) is a fast dog well performed over the sprint races. Last start winner over 457m at Q Lakeside in a Grade 4/5 (25.43) and less ground suits even better. Goes very well here at the trip finding the frame in each of six starts. Significant danger. BENTLEY OLAF (8) was in the money two back in a OPEN at Rockhampton then jumped from a squeeze draw last time and was not far away when second (29.63) over 510m at Rockhampton.",
